                             </p>
                                                      <p>
                                              <em>Vija Celmins: Dessins/Drawings</em>, exh. cat., Centre National d'Art et de Culture Georges Pompidou (Paris, 2006), cat. no. 5, repr. p. 49
                             </p>
                                                      <p>
                                              Gary Garrels, <em>Vija Celmins: To Fix the Image in Memory</em>, exh. cat., San Francisco Museum of Art and Yale University Press (San Francisco, New Haven and London, 2018), pp. 51, 263, ill. (color)
