                            </p>
                          <p>
                              <em>Vija Celmins</em>, Institute of Contemporary Art, Philadelphia, Philadelphia, 11/06/1992 - 01/17/1993; Henry Art Gallery, Seattle, 03/03/1993 - 05/23/1993; Walker Art Center, Minneapolis, 06/08/1993 - 09/08/1993; Whitney Museum of American Art, New York, 09/17/1993 - 11/29/1993; Museum of Contemporary Art, Los Angeles, Los Angeles, 12/19/1993 - 02/06/1994
                            </p>
                          <p>
                              <em>Vija Celmins - A Retrospective; Works 1964-1996</em>, Museo Nacional Centro de Arte Reina Sofia, Madrid, 01/21/1997 - 03/23/1997; Kunstmuseum Winterthur, Winterthur, 04/12/1997 - 06/15/1997
                            </p>
                          <p>
                              <em>Photography into Painting, Work on Paper</em>, Carpenter Center for the Visual Arts, Cambridge, 12/05/1996 - 12/28/1996
                            </p>
                          <p>
                              <em>A Decade of Collecting: Recent Acquisitions of Prints and Drawings from 1940 to 2000</em>, Harvard University Art Museums, Cambridge, 06/03/2000 - 08/27/2000
                            </p>
                          <p>
                              <em>The Prints of Vija Celmins</em>, The Metropolitan Museum of Art, New York, 10/15/2002 - 12/29/2002
                            </p>
                          <p>
                              <em>Nominally Figured: Recent Acquisitions in Contemporary Art</em>, Harvard University Art Museums, Cambridge, 06/08/2006 - 02/25/2007
                            </p>
                          <p>
                              <em>Vija Celmins: A Drawings Retrospective/Vija Celmins: L'oeuvre dessiné</em>, Centre National d'Art et de Culture Georges Pompidou, Paris Cedex 04, 10/25/2006 - 01/08/2007; Armand Hammer Museum of Art and Cultural Center, Los Angeles, 01/28/2007 - 04/22/2007
                            </p>
                          <p>
                              <em>32Q: 3620 University Study Gallery</em>, Harvard Art Museums, Cambridge, 08/25/2015 - 10/05/2015
                            </p>
                          <p>
                              <em>Vija Celmins: To Fix the Image of Memory</em>, San Francisco Museum of Modern Art, San Francisco, 12/15/2018 - 03/31/2019
